{"id":651810,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/08/坚果兄弟-｜-自我禁言720小时，招募1000人筹集10万奖金，/","date":"2020-08-05T23:55:02Z","modified":"2020-08-05T23:55:02Z","title":"坚果兄弟 ｜ 自我禁言720小时，招募1000人筹集10万奖金，致谢说真话的记者","content":"<blockquote><p>这是为坚果兄弟最近的项目发的第二篇征集：「真话冒险奖」。</p>\n<p>我和坚果兄弟相识多年，时不时会交流一些彼此的创作和创作遇到的问题。最早在北京认识是因为他那著名的《尘埃计划》，用吸尘器吸北京的雾霾最后做成一块砖，摆放在了某条胡同一个正在建造的小房子里。坚果兄弟产量非常高，每年都有好几个事儿在做，每一个都直插社会事件核心，刚硬有力，态度鲜明。前几天发布的<a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4NDAwMzkzMQ==&amp;mid=2649707077&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=3bf184f82f7e8e16269b3561093f46ac&amp;chksm=87f62f71b081a667ee24fcb8a84ecf415ccbc4f413f7fb95c06275632f6b130ce703807f3d8a&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\">《自我举报试验》</a><em>（点击查看）</em>还差一半人就可达到目标。感兴趣的请加坚果兄弟微信：jianguoxiongdi</p>\n<p>沈博伦</p></blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>大家好，我是坚果兄弟。我想设立一个「真话冒险奖」，为新冠疫情期间说真话的记者。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-651812\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟1-11-300x213.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"356\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟1-11-300x213.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟1-11-1024x728.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟1-11-768x546.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟1-11-400x284.jpg 400w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟1-11.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>福柯说，“直言”意味着冒险。<strong>今天，说真话尤其是一种冒险。</strong></p>\n<p>这种冒险性依然呼应着50年前索尔仁尼琴说过的一句话：<strong>“</strong><strong>一句真话能比整个世界的分量还重</strong><strong>”</strong>。</p>\n<p>为了致敬在新冠疫情期间无畏且执着挖掘真相的媒体人，我们计划设立“<strong>真话冒险奖</strong>”：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>邀请9位记者组成评委团</li>\n<li>提名并评选出一位说真话的记者。</li>\n<li>奖金：人民币5万元~10万元</li>\n<li>获奖者公布：2020年6月30日</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-651813\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟2-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟2-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟2-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟2-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟2.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>#</strong><strong>闭嘴</strong><strong>720</strong><strong>小时</strong><strong># </strong></p>\n<p><strong>如果不能说真话，我将持续</strong><strong>30</strong><strong>天不说一句话</strong></p>\n<p>从六一儿童节开始直到月底（6月1日下午4点至7月1日下午4点），我将持续1个月，30天，30✘24=720小时，不说一句话。</p>\n<p>“一句真话能比整个世界的分量还重”。我们希望为新冠疫情期间敢说真话的记者设立一个奖项：“真话冒险奖”，但5万元~10万元的奖金迟迟没有着落。</p>\n<p>我们试图通过#闭嘴720小时#这个象征性的行为，与更多支持者发生更深入的精神联结，一起筹集奖项所需要的资金。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-651814\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟3-300x184.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"307\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟3-300x184.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟3-1024x629.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟3-768x471.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟3.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>招募</strong><strong>1000</strong><strong>个联合赞助人</strong></p>\n<p>每位赞助人也是“真话冒险奖”的联合发起人，赞助分以下几档</p>\n<p>A、赞助100元，你将为“真话冒险奖”的设立，进行非常重要的助力和声援；同时，邀请你成为“真话冒险奖”的联合发起人。</p>\n<p>B、赞助500元，邀请你成为“真话冒险奖”的联合发起人。</p>\n<p>C、赞助1000元，邀请你成为“真话冒险奖”的联合发起人。</p>\n<p>D、赞助10000元，邀请你成为“真话冒险奖”的联合发起人。</p>\n<p>E、赞助50000元，邀请你成为“真话冒险奖”的联合发起人。</p>\n<p>★非常感谢你的支援，微信联系：jianguoxiongdi    邮箱：nutbrother@gmail.com</p>\n<p>我是坚果兄弟，曾发起“深圳娃娃”、“北京好运会”、“北京黑话”、“带盐计划”、“无意义公司”、“NBB新闻社”、“尘埃计划”、“防狼喷雾川面馆”、“真相书店”等项目。</p>\n<p>尘埃计划：http://www.jiemian.com/article/464165.html</p>\n<p>带盐计划：https://new.qq.com/omn/20180721/20180721A0H8WJ.html</p>\n<p>★★★所有赞助名单将持续公示：</p>\n<p><strong>乔乔：</strong><strong>100</strong><strong>元</strong></p>\n<p><strong>李二兔：</strong><strong>100</strong><strong>元</strong></p>\n<p><strong>XD</strong><strong>：</strong><strong>100</strong><strong>元</strong></p>\n<p><strong>丁刚：</strong><strong>100</strong><strong>元</strong></p>\n<p><strong>J.Y</strong><strong>：</strong><strong>100</strong><strong>元</strong></p>\n<p><strong>不明白：</strong><strong>100</strong><strong>元</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Jo</strong><strong>：</strong><strong>100</strong><strong>元</strong></p>\n<p><strong>陈嘉：</strong><strong>100</strong><strong>元</strong></p>\n<p><strong>宗文：</strong><strong>500</strong><strong>元</strong></p>\n<p><strong>张洁平：</strong><strong>100</strong><strong>元</strong></p>\n<p><strong>松子：</strong><strong>100</strong><strong>元</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Sailun</strong><strong>：</strong><strong>100</strong><strong>元</strong></p>\n<p><strong>胶囊：</strong><strong>100</strong><strong>元</strong></p>\n<p><strong>烟熏：</strong><strong>100</strong><strong>元</strong></p>\n<p><strong>陆陆：</strong><strong>100</strong><strong>元</strong></p>\n<p><strong>罗拉：</strong><strong>500</strong><strong>元</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Bayar</strong><strong>：</strong><strong>100</strong><strong>元</strong></p>\n<p><strong>莫素匆：</strong><strong>100</strong><strong>元</strong></p>\n<p><strong>刘果：</strong><strong>100</strong><strong>元</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>下面是每天的照片（6.1~6.13）</p>\n<p>从6月1日开始，到今天是第13天。说实话，#闭嘴720小时# ，执行起来，比想象的难。我得承认，到今天为止，我已经憋不住或者下意识说了8句话，我抽了自己14个耳光，外加连续三餐只吃饭不吃菜。（备注：大部分时间贴创可贴或者布条或者不贴，每天照片是一个符号性的拍摄）</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_651815\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-651815\" class=\"wp-image-651815\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟4-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟4-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟4-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟4-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟4.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-651815\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">6月1日</p></div>\n<p>傍晚拍摄时，有一些路人侧目打量，在路上的时候有两个阿姨一直在讨论他为什么贴封条，最后的结论是应该是为了管住嘴，减肥的……</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_651816\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-651816\" class=\"wp-image-651816\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟5-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟5-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟5-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟5.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-651816\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">6月2日</p></div>\n<p>今天下意识接了两句话，给自己用力抽两耳光，一句话一耳光。不闭嘴就得挨打。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_651817\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-651817\" class=\"wp-image-651817\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟6-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟6-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟6-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟6.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-651817\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">6月3日</p></div>\n<p>“冬天他们则穿着木屐走过雪地。这个过程中，僧侣们戴斗笠遮住脸，不和任何人交谈，即使有人问起，也不会道出自己的名字。”</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_651818\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-651818\" class=\"wp-image-651818\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟7-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟7-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟7-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟7-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟7.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-651818\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">6月4日</p></div>\n<p>平时也没有太多话说，但闭嘴后，好像又有不少话说，张了张嘴，发现被创可贴封住了。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_651819\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-651819\" class=\"wp-image-651819\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟8-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟8-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟8-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟8-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟8.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-651819\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">6月5日</p></div>\n<p>“只有在这种危险的条件下，才有所谓敢于直言的问题”</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_651820\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-651820\" class=\"wp-image-651820\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟9-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟9-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟9-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟9-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟9.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-651820\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">6月6日</p></div>\n<p>做梦，家族兴衰，洪水开辟新路，丧事，想不起来谁过世。亲人远去。流浪的狗。分不清现实和梦境。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_651821\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-651821\" class=\"wp-image-651821\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟10-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟10-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟10-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟10-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟10.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-651821\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">6月7日</p></div>\n<p>第七天，我开始恐惧见人。人们交谈，用直接语言表达看法、讲述故事、交流观点。我只有自我隔离，说话都是不被充许的，而我很可能不小心说一两句。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-651822\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟11-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟11-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟11-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟11-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟11.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_651823\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-651823\" class=\"wp-image-651823\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟12-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟12-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟12-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟12-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟12.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-651823\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">6月8日</p></div>\n<p>今天中午，一个人在汉堡王看书，自言自语，说了一句话。草，接下来，惩罚自己接下来3餐只吃饭不吃菜。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_651824\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-651824\" class=\"wp-image-651824\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟13-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟13-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟13-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟13-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟13.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-651824\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">6月9日</p></div>\n<p>去知乎上刚发了一篇“闭嘴720小时”，立马被删，账号被炸。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_651825\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-651825\" class=\"wp-image-651825\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟14-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟14-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟14-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟14-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟14.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-651825\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">6月10日</p></div>\n<p>今天下午又不小心接了一句话。抽了一耳光。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-651826\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟15-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟15-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟15-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟15-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟15.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-651827\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟16-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟16-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟16-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟16-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟16.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_651828\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-651828\" class=\"wp-image-651828\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟17-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟17-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟17-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟17-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟17.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-651828\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">6月11日</p></div>\n<p>微博今天被炸了。被持续闭嘴。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_651829\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-651829\" class=\"wp-image-651829\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟18-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟18-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟18-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟18-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟18.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-651829\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">6月12日</p></div>\n<p>一个词，正能量暴力。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_651830\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-651830\" class=\"wp-image-651830\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟19-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟19-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟19-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟19-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟19.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-651830\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">6月13日</p></div>\n<p>如果没有人说真话，媒体也被闭嘴，大众的知情权被剥夺，整个世界被导向狭隘、分裂和暴力，我们离一个包容、多元、和平、民主的世界越来越远。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_651831\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-651831\" class=\"wp-image-651831\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟20-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟20-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟20-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟20-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟20.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-651831\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">6月14日</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_651832\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-651832\" class=\"wp-image-651832\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟21-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/坚果兄弟21-300x200.jpg 300w, htt